                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="p-1">
                        Apply a color to your card using <code class="text-bold text-primary">.card-{color}</code>. Each variant sets the background, border, and text contrast for the whole card.
                        For more specific variations such as colored headers, borders, or hover effects, refer to the examples above.
                    </p>

